title: Hataraku Saibou Lady
alternative_title: Cells at Work! Lady ; はたらく細胞LADY
status: Cells at Work! Lady ; はたらく細胞LADY
description:
Description :
        A story about the inside of a woman's body, dedicated to all living ladies. Menstruation, pregnancy, childbirth, women's specific disorders and diseases. A woman's body is exposed to dizzying changes every day. The ladies' bodies are protected by our immune cells! This is the latest spin-off of the hit cell personification manga *Cells at Work* with a special focus on women!
